#################################################################################################

Drop box is used to backup the project files

Git Repository is used as versioning control

CMake is used to manage the build process

Eclipse is used to code the application using CDT

GNU Auto tools chain is used to compile the application

OpenGL is used to visualise the data

ITK is used to read and create a volume from DICOM Images

